Athena allows HTML authors to describe behavior through markup. It's simple to use, (*http://www.jquery.com*; leverages) (*http://documentcloud.github.com/underscore/*; some of the) (*https://github.com/Jakobo/inject*; best) (*https://github.com/Jakobo/PTClass*; web technologies) some of the best web, and is 100% event driven.
